    Scope and Contents
Student papers and projects of Nelson Howarth's Spring 1972  class on Local Governmental Problems.  The student papers were published together into a booklet entitled  "An Analysis of Five Poblems of Local Governments in the Springfield (Illinois ) Statistical Metropolitan Area."  Subjects include annexation, housing, implementation of the Emergency Employment Act, proliferation of local governments, and recreation.  
  
